divs: Sighting DetailsPhoto taken at a company event. Discovered when photo was enlarged on computer recently. I still work for the company and request all people be blocked out. I have copies of the photo before and after the one with the UFO. This photo was taken by another unknown employee and placed on the company computer. I am in the photo and I have no recollection of any abnormal sounds at the time. This is one of the best UFO photos I've seen and I think it may be good for research and identification.
